  "dialogue": [
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What if you spoke English from morning to night?",
      "zh": "如果你從早到晚都說英語會怎樣？",
      "ja": "朝から晩まで英語を話したらどうなるでしょう？",
      "time": "00:00:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let me show you how.",
      "zh": "讓我來告訴你怎麼做。",
      "ja": "やり方をお見せします。",
      "time": "00:00:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Today we follow one day in my life.",
      "zh": "今天我們跟隨我一天的生活。",
      "ja": "今日は私の一日を追いかけます。",
      "time": "00:00:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Every situation, real English, simple words.",
      "zh": "每個情境，真實英語，簡單單字。",
      "ja": "あらゆる状況で、本物の英語、簡単な言葉を使います。",
      "time": "00:00:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Morning, afternoon, evening.",
      "zh": "早上、下午、晚上。",
      "ja": "朝、昼、夜。",
      "time": "00:00:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You will learn English for all of them.",
      "zh": "你將學會這些時間的英語。",
      "ja": "それぞれの時間帯の英語を学びます。",
      "time": "00:00:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Repeat every sentence out loud.",
      "zh": "大聲重複每句話。",
      "ja": "すべての文を声に出して繰り返してください。",
      "time": "00:00:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "This is your speaking practice for today.",
      "zh": "這是你今天的口說練習。",
      "ja": "これが今日のスピーキング練習です。",
      "time": "00:00:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let's go!",
      "zh": "開始吧！",
      "ja": "さあ、始めましょう！",
      "time": "00:00:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's seven in the morning, time to wake up.",
      "zh": "現在是早上七點，該起床了。",
      "ja": "朝の7時、起きる時間です。",
      "time": "00:00:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm so tired, five more minutes.",
      "zh": "我好累，再睡五分鐘。",
      "ja": "とても疲れた、あと5分だけ。",
      "time": "00:00:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Good morning!",
      "zh": "早安！",
      "ja": "おはようございます！",
      "time": "00:00:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What a beautiful day.",
      "zh": "多美好的一天。",
      "ja": "なんて美しい日でしょう。",
      "time": "00:00:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Repeat after me.",
      "zh": "跟我重複。",
      "ja": "私の後に繰り返してください。",
      "time": "00:00:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I always make coffee in the morning.",
      "zh": "我早上總是煮咖啡。",
      "ja": "私はいつも朝にコーヒーを淹れます。",
      "time": "00:00:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I can't start my day without it.",
      "zh": "沒有它我無法開始一天。",
      "ja": "それなしでは一日を始められません。",
      "time": "00:00:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let me check my messages.",
      "zh": "讓我看看訊息。",
      "ja": "メッセージをチェックします。",
      "time": "00:00:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, I have a lot of emails today.",
      "zh": "喔，今天有很多郵件。",
      "ja": "ああ、今日はメールがたくさんあります。",
      "time": "00:00:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "In the morning I always say these phrases.",
      "zh": "早上我總是說這些句子。",
      "ja": "朝はいつもこれらのフレーズを言います。",
      "time": "00:00:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Repeat after me.",
      "zh": "跟我重複。",
      "ja": "私の後に繰り返してください。",
      "time": "00:00:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I need to get ready.",
      "zh": "我需要準備了。",
      "ja": "準備しなければなりません。",
      "time": "00:00:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm running late.",
      "zh": "我快遲到了。",
      "ja": "遅れそうです。",
      "time": "00:01:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm on my way.",
      "zh": "我在路上了。",
      "ja": "向かっています。",
      "time": "00:01:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "OK.",
      "zh": "好的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:01:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm ready.",
      "zh": "我準備好了。",
      "ja": "準備できました。",
      "time": "00:01:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Time to start the day.",
      "zh": "該開始一天了。",
      "ja": "一日を始める時間です。",
      "time": "00:01:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let's go!",
      "zh": "出發！",
      "ja": "行きましょう！",
      "time": "00:01:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Great job!",
      "zh": "做得好！",
      "ja": "よくできました！",
      "time": "00:01:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You just learned morning English.",
      "zh": "你剛學會了早晨英語。",
      "ja": "朝の英語を学びました。",
      "time": "00:01:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Now, lunch time!",
      "zh": "現在，午餐時間！",
      "ja": "さて、ランチタイムです！",
      "time": "00:01:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm meeting my friend Chloe for lunch today.",
      "zh": "今天我要和朋友Chloe吃午餐。",
      "ja": "今日は友達のクロエとランチをします。",
      "time": "00:01:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hey Chloe, sorry I'm late.",
      "zh": "嗨Chloe，抱歉我遲到了。",
      "ja": "やあクロエ、遅れてごめん。",
      "time": "00:01:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The traffic was terrible.",
      "zh": "交通很糟。",
      "ja": "交通がひどかったんだ。",
      "time": "00:01:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No worries.",
      "zh": "沒關係。",
      "ja": "気にしないで。",
      "time": "00:01:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I just got here too.",
      "zh": "我也剛到。",
      "ja": "私も今着いたところです。",
      "time": "00:01:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Are you ready to order?",
      "zh": "你準備好點餐了嗎？",
      "ja": "注文の準備はできましたか？",
      "time": "00:01:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Almost.",
      "zh": "差不多了。",
      "ja": "もう少しです。",
      "time": "00:01:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Can I have one more minute, please?",
      "zh": "可以再給我一分鐘嗎？",
      "ja": "もう1分いただけますか？",
      "time": "00:01:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "A few moments later.",
      "zh": "幾分鐘後。",
      "ja": "数分後。",
      "time": "00:01:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'll have the chicken sandwich and a glass of water, please.",
      "zh": "我要一份雞肉三明治和一杯水，謝謝。",
      "ja": "チキンサンドイッチと水を一杯ください。",
      "time": "00:01:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Use I'll have when you order food.",
      "zh": "點餐時用 I'll have。",
      "ja": "食べ物を注文するときは I'll have を使います。",
      "time": "00:01:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Very natural.",
      "zh": "非常自然。",
      "ja": "とても自然です。",
      "time": "00:01:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "How are you?",
      "zh": "你好嗎？",
      "ja": "お元気ですか？",
      "time": "00:01:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You look tired.",
      "zh": "你看起來很累。",
      "ja": "疲れているようですね。",
      "time": "00:01:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I know.",
      "zh": "我知道。",
      "ja": "そうですね。",
      "time": "00:01:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I've been so busy lately.",
      "zh": "我最近很忙。",
      "ja": "最近とても忙しいです。",
      "time": "00:01:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Work is crazy right now.",
      "zh": "工作現在很瘋狂。",
      "ja": "仕事が今とても大変です。",
      "time": "00:01:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "At the cafe you need these phrases.",
      "zh": "在咖啡廳你需要這些句子。",
      "ja": "カフェで使うフレーズです。",
      "time": "00:02:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Repeat.",
      "zh": "跟我重複。",
      "ja": "繰り返してください。",
      "time": "00:02:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Could we get the bill, please?",
      "zh": "請給我們帳單，好嗎？",
      "ja": "お会計をお願いします。",
      "time": "00:02:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let's split the bill.",
      "zh": "我們分開付帳。",
      "ja": "割り勘にしましょう。",
      "time": "00:02:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It was delicious.",
      "zh": "很好吃。",
      "ja": "美味しかったです。",
      "time": "00:02:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "zh": "謝謝。",
      "ja": "ありがとうございます。",
      "time": "00:02:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Perfect.",
      "zh": "完美。",
      "ja": "完璧です。",
      "time": "00:02:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You can now order food in English.",
      "zh": "你現在可以用英語點餐了。",
      "ja": "これで英語で注文できます。",
      "time": "00:02:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Next, work.",
      "zh": "接下來是工作。",
      "ja": "次は仕事です。",
      "time": "00:02:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Back to work.",
      "zh": "回到工作。",
      "ja": "仕事に戻ります。",
      "time": "00:02:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Time to be professional.",
      "zh": "是時候專業一點了。",
      "ja": "プロフェッショナルになる時間です。",
      "time": "00:02:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Good afternoon.",
      "zh": "午安。",
      "ja": "こんにちは。",
      "time": "00:02:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "This is Sophia speaking.",
      "zh": "我是Sophia。",
      "ja": "ソフィアが話しています。",
      "time": "00:02:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "How can I help you?",
      "zh": "我能幫你什麼？",
      "ja": "どうされましたか？",
      "time": "00:02:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Sophia, can you send me that report?",
      "zh": "Sophia，你能寄給我那份報告嗎？",
      "ja": "ソフィア、そのレポートを送ってもらえますか？",
      "time": "00:02:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Of course.",
      "zh": "當然。",
      "ja": "もちろんです。",
      "time": "00:02:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'll send it right away.",
      "zh": "我馬上寄出。",
      "ja": "すぐに送ります。",
      "time": "00:02:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm sorry, could you repeat that?",
      "zh": "抱歉，你能再說一次嗎？",
      "ja": "すみません、もう一度言ってもらえますか？",
      "time": "00:02:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The connection is not very good.",
      "zh": "連線不太好。",
      "ja": "接続があまり良くありません。",
      "time": "00:02:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Very useful in online meetings.",
      "zh": "在線上會議中非常有用。",
      "ja": "オンライン会議でとても役立ちます。",
      "time": "00:02:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That's it for today's meetings.",
      "zh": "今天的會議就到這裡。",
      "ja": "今日の会議はこれで終わりです。",
      "time": "00:02:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm exhausted.",
      "zh": "我累壞了。",
      "ja": "疲れました。",
      "time": "00:02:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "At work in English, you need these.",
      "zh": "工作時你需要這些英語句子。",
      "ja": "仕事で使う英語フレーズです。",
      "time": "00:03:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Repeat after me.",
      "zh": "跟我重複。",
      "ja": "私の後に繰り返してください。",
      "time": "00:03:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let me get back to you on that.",
      "zh": "我稍後回覆你。",
      "ja": "後でご連絡します。",
      "time": "00:03:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'll take care of it.",
      "zh": "我會處理的。",
      "ja": "私が対応します。",
      "time": "00:03:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Could we schedule a meeting?",
      "zh": "我們可以安排會議嗎？",
      "ja": "ミーティングを予定できますか？",
      "time": "00:03:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Work is done.",
      "zh": "工作完成了。",
      "ja": "仕事が終わりました。",
      "time": "00:03:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Now the best part.",
      "zh": "現在是最棒的部分。",
      "ja": "さて、一番いい時間です。",
      "time": "00:03:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Evening at home.",
      "zh": "晚上在家。",
      "ja": "家での夜。",
      "time": "00:03:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Finally home, this is my favorite part of the day.",
      "zh": "終於回家了，這是我一天中最喜歡的時刻。",
      "ja": "やっと家に帰りました。これが一日の中で一番好きな時間です。",
      "time": "00:03:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I love cooking in the evening.",
      "zh": "我喜歡晚上做飯。",
      "ja": "夜に料理をするのが好きです。",
      "time": "00:03:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It helps me relax.",
      "zh": "這讓我放鬆。",
      "ja": "リラックスできます。",
      "time": "00:03:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "How was your day?",
      "zh": "你今天過得怎麼樣？",
      "ja": "今日はいかがでしたか？",
      "time": "00:03:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Pretty busy, but good.",
      "zh": "相當忙碌，但還不錯。",
      "ja": "かなり忙しかったけど、良かったです。",
      "time": "00:03:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I had lunch with Chloe.",
      "zh": "我和Chloe吃了午餐。",
      "ja": "クロエとランチをしました。",
      "time": "00:03:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Are you eating well?",
      "zh": "你吃得好嗎？",
      "ja": "ちゃんと食べていますか？",
      "time": "00:03:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes, don't worry.",
      "zh": "是的，別擔心。",
      "ja": "はい、大丈夫です。",
      "time": "00:03:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm making pasta right now.",
      "zh": "我現在正在做義大利麵。",
      "ja": "今パスタを作っています。",
      "time": "00:03:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That's my girl.",
      "zh": "乖孩子。",
      "ja": "いい子だね。",
      "time": "00:03:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "After dinner, I like to watch something in English.",
      "zh": "晚餐後，我喜歡看英文節目。",
      "ja": "夕食後は英語の何かを見るのが好きです。",
      "time": "00:03:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's good practice.",
      "zh": "這是很好的練習。",
      "ja": "良い練習になります。",
      "time": "00:03:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Evening phrases.",
      "zh": "晚間用語。",
      "ja": "夜のフレーズ。",
      "time": "00:04:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The ones you use every night.",
      "zh": "你每天晚上都會用的句子。",
      "ja": "毎晩使うフレーズです。",
      "time": "00:04:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Repeat.",
      "zh": "跟我重複。",
      "ja": "繰り返してください。",
      "time": "00:04:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm going to call it a night.",
      "zh": "我要休息了。",
      "ja": "もう寝ます。",
      "time": "00:04:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "This means I'm going to sleep now.",
      "zh": "這表示我要睡覺了。",
      "ja": "これは今から寝るという意味です。",
      "time": "00:04:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I had a long day.",
      "zh": "我今天很累。",
      "ja": "長い一日でした。",
      "time": "00:04:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Sleep well, sweet dreams.",
      "zh": "睡個好覺，做個好夢。",
      "ja": "よく眠って、いい夢を。",
      "time": "00:04:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And that's a full day in English.",
      "zh": "這就是用英語度過的一整天。",
      "ja": "これが英語で過ごす一日です。",
      "time": "00:04:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let's review everything now.",
